===Etymology===
From {{inh|en|enm|scabard}}, {{m|enm|scauberde}}, {{m|enm|scauberk}}, {{m|enm|scauberke}}, from {{der|en|xno|eschaubert}}, {{m|fro|escalberc}}, of {{der|en|gem}} origin, perhaps from {{der|en|frk|*skarberg|t=sheath|lit=blade-protection}}, from {{der|en|gem-pro|*skēriz|t=blade, scissors}} + {{m|gem-pro|*bergaz|t=shelter, protection, refuge}}. See also {{m|en|hauberk}}.

